10 ounce Pork Tenderloin
1 teaspoon Chili & Ginger Spice Rub
1.75 ounce Spicy Ginger-Lime Aïoli
6 ounce Broccoli
2.13 ounce Yellow Onions & Ginger
1 teaspoon Black & White Sesame Seeds
5.25 ounce Cabbage & Carrots
1.25 ounce Ginger-Lime Vinaigrette
½ ounce Almonds
Cooking Oil
Salt
Pepper

Please refer to the recipe card for Step 1.